{"tid":167794,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"點解呢一代人會過得咁艱難？","createTime":"2017-03-23T05:44:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-23T11:17:35.000Z","uid":78492,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"17e113840fd172ecb7609c19a884286ccbdfa853","tid":167794,"uid":78492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T05:44:50.000Z","msg":"到底由幾時開始，呢個世界好似變得生活艱難左好多。以前政府或私人企業都會有長俸，人工又會每年加，但依家就無左呢支歌仔唱。<br />\n<br />\n我問一個退休十幾年既公務員（退休時人工兩萬幾，現時每月有萬零蚊長俸）如果佢依家打工有沒信心置業，佢都好肯定咁答我：無可能。<br />\n<br />\n到底問題出係邊度？"},{"pid":"f96f63d6d00fb3d98601601e3da0568f11515a3c","tid":167794,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T05:46:11.000Z","msg":"因為你廢<br />\n<br />\n邊個時代都好<br />\n<br />\n始終有人生活開心富貴"},{"pid":"ba9d6ff69c9a2e39ae1517ffd7ff43d645115271","tid":167794,"uid":78492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T05:48:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>因為你廢<br />\n<br />\n邊個時代都好<br />\n<br />\n始終有人生活開心富貴</blockquote><br />\n因為呢一代人廢，所以全部人轉晒行新制？"},{"pid":"23ebbe4bb74d712d266b947e1128001b90a59f14","tid":167794,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T05:48:30.000Z","msg":"等睇連登廢人賴地硬<br />\n<br />\n怨天怨地<br />\n<br />\n但從來唔反省自己廢"},{"pid":"5cb47f3ac2424a5555e17126b748537193d1f02c","tid":167794,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T05:49:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>因為你廢<br />\n<br />\n邊個時代都好<br />\n<br />\n始終有人生活開心富貴</blockquote><br />\n因為呢一代人廢，所以全部人轉晒行新制？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n原來就係新制害到你挨苦？<br />\n<br />\n你咁撚慘呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5e2d0e89a17cb77dd37f96efdf0a818d85f609b","tid":167794,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T05:51:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>等睇連登廢人賴地硬<br />\n<br />\n怨天怨地<br />\n<br />\n但從來唔反省自己廢</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個個都劍橋 grad但搵唔到工"},{"pid":"18e7